{"tid":1220734,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【送中惡法】搶示威者旗有一千獎金 蛇頭：見到人有錢收","createTime":"2019-06-14T05:15:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T06:15:36.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a738da3e2c9869c409d0aaa030e01f05b4b04769","tid":1220734,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T05:15:12.000Z","msg":"近日有市民向本刊透露指，有應用程式群組聘請年輕人參與近日「反送中」示威遊行，除了底薪更有獎金。有參與過其中的年輕人指，搶走示威者旗幟就可賺一千元，自己有朋友搶了約五支旗，連底薪共賺六千元。<br />\n<br />\n市民陳先生指，過去有讚好一個社交網站專頁，有討論各式娛樂話題的群組。「有些是討論賭波賭馬的群組，有些是閒聊、東拉西扯的群組，古靈精怪的片段又有一個群組，很大規模的。」他說，及後他被誤加入招聘遊行人士的群組。詢問之下，他發現該群組正在招攬六月十一日晚的「搞事人」。他更發現群組中「應徵」的大部分是年輕人，大多數為十七、八歲，有部分為二十二、三歲。<br />\n<br />\n「全部都是小朋友， 看他們都是為了錢而出來。」陳先生認為。他又透露曾接觸一名參與招聘遊行的年輕人，對方指自己過去於六月九日反送中大遊行中，搶去示威者的幾支旗幟，每支可賺一千元；有朋友搶了四、五支，加上出席底薪就可賺近六千元。<br />\n<br />\n本刊記者聯絡該群組版主，他竟指每次遊行只需拍照，就可賺六百元。記者進一步詢問後加入該群組，並相約六月十一日晚上前往「反送中」的示威活動，對方更表示「見到人就有錢收」，更可帶同「話頭醒尾」的朋友一同工作。但陳先生表示，曾目擊有人詢問如何「出糧」後，被負責人質問來歷，就立即並被管理員踢出群組。<br />\n<br />\n六月十一日晚上，記者於灣與群組仔集合點集合後，發現所有參與人士均為男士，年齡約十八至二十二歲。及後當日有年輕負責人因性別而質疑記者來歷，經多次質問後經誰介紹，記者表示是經朋友介紹群組版主，對方竟突然稱「我們只是相約吃飯」，並無其他目的。及後群組版主聯絡記者，表示因性別問題而需要暫停工作。<br />\n<br />\n「我不知道你是女士，女士就不需要了。」群組版主表示，及後記者於群組中被刪去。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/nextplus/magazine/article/20190614/2_675628_0/-%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD%E6%83%A1%E6%B3%95-%E6%90%B6%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E6%97%97%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%80%E5%8D%83%E7%8D%8E%E9%87%91-%E8%9B%87%E9%A0%AD-%E8%A6%8B%E5%88%B0%E4%BA%BA%E6%9C%89%E9%8C%A2%E6%94%B6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Fnextplus%2Fmagazine%2Farticle%2F20190614%2F2_675628_0%2F-%25E9%2580%2581%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%2583%25A1%25E6%25B3%2595-%25E6%2590%25B6%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2580%2585%25E6%2597%2597%25E6%259C%2589%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%258D%2583%25E7%258D%258E%25E9%2587%2591-%25E8%259B%2587%25E9%25A0%25AD-%25E8%25A6%258B%25E5%2588%25B0%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%259C%2589%25E9%258C%25A2%25E6%2594%25B6&d=yztsqsfTIdfogAH81g8uWP3PLjr3aI%2Bxco%2FW%2FCjCBac%3D&h=9bedf06d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Fnextplus%2Fmagazine%2Farticle%2F20190614%2F2_675628_0%2F-%25E9%2580%2581%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%2583%25A1%25E6%25B3%2595-%25E6%2590%25B6%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2580%2585%25E6%2597%2597%25E6%259C%2589%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%258D%2583%25E7%258D%258E%25E9%2587%2591-%25E8%259B%2587%25E9%25A0%25AD-%25E8%25A6%258B%25E5%2588%25B0%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%259C%2589%25E9%258C%25A2%25E6%2594%25B6&h=55bc0e36\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/nextplus/magazine/article/20190614/2_675628_0/-%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD%E6%83%A1%E6%B3%95-%E6%90%B6%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E6%97%97%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%80%E5%8D%83%E7%8D%8E%E9%87%91-%E8%9B%87%E9%A0%AD-%E8%A6%8B%E5%88%B0%E4%BA%BA%E6%9C%89%E9%8C%A2%E6%94%B6</a><br />\n<br />\n有冇人可以查吓到底呢堆咩人嚟??"},{"pid":"5ad775dc8cec9fb19b7b4634c1da8406ef360fa6","tid":1220734,"uid":160051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T05:20:24.000Z","msg":"咁即啲旗拎去賺錢都好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4df04da2413549655ef8cccb038c111626e9729","tid":1220734,"uid":20291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T05:26:28.000Z","msg":"我2百得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7021ead5a7af8ba63b345c5380259067ce67f17","tid":1220734,"uid":20291,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d4df04da2413549655ef8cccb038c111626e9729","tid":1220734,"uid":20291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T05:26:28.000Z","msg":"我2百得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T05:26:58.000Z","msg":"食煙食彈加多20下午茶算"},{"pid":"e19eec294239ffc2f6be8660d98b8af7560e0828","tid":1220734,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T06:01:29.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d77a1b84f65a9af3612d9f24010fdb859fd38a81","tid":1220734,"uid":145823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T06:04:36.000Z","msg":"交收完再拎嚟買物資 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b05609761fe4be232b354f4e694b4bb6d7704526","tid":1220734,"uid":9053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T06:14:39.000Z","msg":"問題係哪兒來的旗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97619b70a9d94a4fa6b70ee4bb175f1741da15b3","tid":1220734,"uid":8858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T06:15:36.000Z","msg":"發達大計裡應外合搵晒啲錢"}]}